{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"767","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"半導體點火 7月製造業生產指數創歷年同月新高","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>最新更新：<span lang='EN-US'>2020/08/24 18:28</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 532px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經濟部統計處<span lang='EN-US'>24</span>日公布工業生產指數，其中製造業生產指數<span lang='EN-US'>116.35</span>，年增<span lang='EN-US'>2.64%</span>，是歷年同月新高。（中央社檔案照片）</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p style='text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>（中央社記者梁珮綺台北<span lang='EN-US'>24</span>日電）半導體產業持續點火，帶動工業生產動能，<span lang='EN-US'>7</span>月工業生產指數年增<span lang='EN-US'>2.65%</span>，連續第<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>個月正成長，其中，製造業生產指數<span lang='EN-US'>116.35</span>，年增<span lang='EN-US'>2.64%</span>，是歷年同月新高。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>經濟部統計處今天公布工業生產指數<span lang='EN-US'>116.70</span>，年增<span lang='EN-US'>2.65%</span>，為歷年單月第<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>高，其中，製造業生產指數<span lang='EN-US'>116.35</span>，年增<span lang='EN-US'>2.64%</span>，是歷年同月新高，兩者也是連續第<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>個月正成長。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>統計處副處長黃偉傑分析，電子零組件業指數為<span lang='EN-US'>132.80</span>，為歷年單月第<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>高，年增<span lang='EN-US'>14.42%</span>，也是連續第<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>個月二位數成長，也是推升製造業成長主力，其中，積體電路業受惠<span lang='EN-US'>5G</span>通訊、高效能運算、物聯網等應用持續推展，加上遠距商機帶動晶圓代工生產，年增<span lang='EN-US'>22.01%</span>，創歷年同月新高，也是連續第<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>個月正成長。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>而液晶面板及組建業年增<span lang='EN-US'>7.07%</span>，主因電視品牌廠拉貨動能回溫、<span lang='EN-US'>IT</span>面板需求暢旺、彩色濾光片、<span lang='EN-US'>LCD</span>用玻璃基板連帶增產所致。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>黃偉傑說，遠距需求發酵，激勵伺服器、筆電生產暢旺，加上網通設備在國內產能擴增，電腦電子產品及光學製品業年增<span lang='EN-US'>12.80%</span>，創歷年單月新高，也是連續第<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>個月正成長。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>傳統產業中，機械業因半導體生產設備受惠大廠產能擴增，減幅收斂，年減<span lang='EN-US'>3.49%</span>。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>不過，其他傳產如石油及煤製品業、紡織業、基本金屬業、金屬製品業及化學原材料業受疫情影響，市場需求仍相當疲弱，加上部分產業進行維修，分別年減<span lang='EN-US'>26.52%</span>、<span lang='EN-US'>22.10%</span>、<span lang='EN-US'>14.03%</span>、<span lang='EN-US'>5.94%</span>及<span lang='EN-US'>1.75%</span>。</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>展望未來，黃偉傑認為，隨著各品牌行動裝置新品接續上市，加上<span lang='EN-US'>5G</span>通訊、高效能運算、物聯網等需求強勁，可望挹注資訊及電子產業生產動能，然而，疫情及美中貿易戰加深國際經濟不確定性，加上國內烯烴廠及鋼鐵大廠高爐歲修，恐抑制傳產生產表現。（編輯：林興盟）<span lang='EN-US'>1090824</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'><span style='font-size:18px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202008240228.aspx</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='text-align: justify;'>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-08-25","clk_count":"197"}},"__N_SSG":true}